r de cura o que era de fato a manipulação do tempo._#','#_Некоторые природные маги, не сознавая последствий, воспользовались энергией времени, вихри которой все еще кружат над Доминарией. То, что они приняли за целебную магию, на самом деле было манипуляцией времени._#','#_Algunos magos de la naturaleza sin saberlo sacaron provecho de las energías temporales que aún rondaban por Dominaria. Lo que confundieron con magia de curación era en realidad manipulación del tiempo._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('130702','Yixlid Jailer','FUT','Creature — Zombie Wizard','U','{1}{B}','2','2','1',NULL,'Cards in graveyards lose all abilities.','#_"I have an eternity to know the souls who are bound here, to behold their every facet. But moments from now they will be gagged and masked, and they shall be known by none other."_#',NULL,'Matt Cavotta','93','4.424','£5/1/2007: This removes all abilities on all cards in all graveyards — both the ones that matter in a graveyard (dredge, Chronosavant’s ability, etc.) and those that don’t.£5/1/2007: If an ability triggers when the object that has it is put into a graveyard from the battlefield, that ability triggers from the battlefield (such as Deadwood Treefolk or Epochrasite, for example), they won’t be affected by Yixlid Jailer.£5/1/2007: If an ability triggers when the object that has it is put into a graveyard from anywhere other than the battlefield, that ability triggers from the graveyard, (such as Krosan Tusker, Narcomoeba, or Quagnoth, for example). Yixlid Jailer will prevent those abilities from triggering at all.£5/1/2007: If an ability triggers when the object that has it is put into a hidden zone from a graveyard, that ability triggers from the graveyard, (such as Golgari Brownscale), Yixlid Jailer will prevent that ability from triggering.£5/1/2007: Some replacement effects cause a card to be put somewhere else instead of being put into a graveyard (such as Legacy Weapon). These effects mean the card is never actually put into the graveyard, so Yixlid Jailer can’t affect it.£5/1/2007: Some cards have abilities that modify how they’re put onto the battlefield. For example, Scarwood Treefolk says “Scarwood Treefolk is put onto the battlefield tapped” and Triskelion says “Triskelion enters the battlefield with three +1/+1 counters on it.” Although these cards won’t have these abilities in the graveyard, they will be applied if the cards are put onto the battlefield from the graveyard (due to Zombify, perhaps). What matters is that these cards will have these abilities on the battlefield.£5/1/2007: If Mistform Ultimus is in the graveyard, the Ultimus will lose its ability that says “Mistform Ultimus is every creature type,” but it will still *be* all creature types. The way continuous effects work, Mistform Ultimus’s type-changing ability is applied before Yixlid Jailer’s ability removes it.','B',NULL,'0.08','0.34','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'B','异西里狱卒',NULL,'Gardien de prison yixlide','Yixlid-Kerkermeister','Carceriere Yixlid','イクスリッドの看守','Carcereiro Yixlid','Икслидский Тюремщик','Carcelero yixlid',NULL,'生物～灵俑／法术师',NULL,'Créature : zombie et sorcier','Kreatur — Zombie, Zauberer','Creatura — Mago Zombie','クリーチャー ― ゾンビ・ウィザード','Criatura — Mago Zumbi','Существо — Зомби Чародей','Criatura — Hechicero zombie',NULL,'在坟墓场中的牌均失去所有异能。',NULL,'Les cartes dans les cimetières perdent toutes leurs capacités.','Karten auf Friedhöfen verlieren alle Fähigkeiten.','Le carte nei cimiteri perdono tutte le abilità.','墓地にあるカードはすべての能力を失う。','Cards em cemitérios perdem todas as habilidades.','Находящиеся на кладбищах карты теряют все свои способности.','Las cartas en los cementerios pierden todas sus habilidades.',NULL,'#_「我有用不尽的时间来认识拘留于此者，摸清一切底细。 但从现在开始，他们将塞口覆面，从此无人得识。」_#',NULL,'#_« J''ai l''éternité pour connaître les âmes emprisonnées dans ces lieux, pour étudier chacune de leurs facettes. Mais dans quelques instants, elles seront masquées et muselées, et personne d''autre ne